<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann von Hohenlohe</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Eberhard Has, Diener der Stadt, wegen Andreas Imhoff, Bürger zu Nürnberg, und seines Dieners an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_79" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_79_r2l32"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hanſen von Hohenloch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r2l33"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wer <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> gevvalt hat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_79_r2l34">Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> vvir ſenden cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>hart</expan> <expan>haſe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnſern dıener mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r2l35">ewr Edell cʒureden von Andreſen Jm hofe / vnd ſeins dieners vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_79_r2l36">vnd Rogamus vvas derſelb etc ut in foꝛma <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_79" id="38r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hansen von Hohenloch
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> wer <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt
                        hat </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, wir senden czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Eb<ex>er</ex>hart</expan>
<expan>Hase<ex>n</ex></expan>, unsern diener, mit ewr edell czureden von Andresen Im
            Hofe und seins dieners wegen und rogamus, was derselb etc. ut in forma.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Petri et Pauli
            <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>lo<ex>rum</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
